		<td class="smallfont"><b>article about why EQ was so succesful and how WoW could be :)</b></td>
		<td class="smallfont" align="right" wrap="nowrap">Post #<b><a href="showpost.php?s=cce877e6623a18e61cf243d19379fb11&amp;postid=222644&postcount=1" target="new">1</a></b></td>
