</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Blizzard hasn't made a MMORPG yet.  They made Diablo - a hideously successful and quality game of its genre.  They made the warcraft/starcraft series - tremendously successful and quality RTS games.  I have little doubt that they'll do as phenomenal a job in this genre as they've done in the others.  Blizzard programmers PLAY GAMES.  We all know that the people in charge of making decisions for the shaman class in EQ do NOT play the game....  This in itself gives me hope.<br />
<br />
All in all, hearty applause for the article.  I think some of his comments were over the top, but his conclusions were bullseyes.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
