	<!-- message -->
	<p>Folks honestly you are all smarter and more skilled than you think.  This is almost like the old "I would not be a member of a club that would have me for a member."<br />
<br />
Compared to most other games, hobbies, activites EQ is pretty difficult.  The vast number of items and skill and content in the game demands that one has to be pretty good at sorting out the complexities of the game.<br />
<br />
Just think how hard the game would be IF we did not have extra-Sony resources like this message board?  I can remember four years ago when I was not savvy to using other websites to gain some advantage and my character was hitting a wall.  I don't think I am an idiot and I found the game to be pretty difficult.  One of us saying EQ is not hard is like Bobby Fisher saying Chess is easy.  Of course Bobby Fisher has said stranger things.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
