	<!-- message -->
	<p>In the beginning, EQ was much harder than it is now. There were no big sites to look up information. There was no insta-travel to anywhere you please. The game has become dumbed down quite a bit, and continues to do so. Can't blame SOE, though, I think it attracts more players that way. And there is still enough challanging content to keep most of the "smarter" players happy/</p>
	
	
	
