</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I agree EQ is a challenging game and it is something I really enjoy about it, but the exetremely long camp times to do anything is well - awful.<br />
<br />
Go to a named spot, find the ph clear the area for hours hoping the named you want will pop and if and when it pops hope that it will drop what you are looking for.<br />
<br />
Need faction for a hand in or something else be prepared to do hours/days of killing the same mob over and over for small changes.<br />
<br />
Need a key, spell anything - <br />
<br />
Hard and challenging is not the same as repetitive and boring.<br />
<br />
EQ has both, get rid of the camping and I'd play EQ forever.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
